headline: Incyte to Report Fourth Quarter and Year-End 2025 Financial Results
summary: WILMINGTON, Del., January 27, 2026--Incyte (Nasdaq:INCY) announced today that it has scheduled its fourth quarter and year-end 2025 financial results conference call and webcast for 8:00 a.m. ET on Tuesday, February 10, 2026.

headline: 2 Profitable Stocks Worth Investigating and 1 We Turn Down
summary: While profitability is essential, it doesn’t guarantee long-term success. Some companies that rest on their margins will lose ground as competition intensifies - as Jeff Bezos said, "Your margin is my opportunity".
